- The Carousel XL -
Sound design by @kitchenshelf 

This is one of the five large (digital) outdoor installations that will be included in my upcoming drop on @niftygateway this Monday (June 21). There will also be a smaller interior version available. The artwork is based upon the 'Trammel of Archimedes' mechanism, featuring the 'Crouching Boy' sculpture by Michelangelo.
.
.
.
.

node.text:
I’m very excited to announce my next drop on @niftygateway, this Monday (June 21).

I call this series ‘Proportions’ and it’s an exploration in how we perceive scale in digital art. It’s a collection of five looping sculptures that comes in the shape of both small interior objects and larger exterior installations.

The drop will include 5 drawings (editions of 10) and 5 single edition artworks.
If you’re interested in collecting a piece, make sure to set up your account beforehand on www.niftygateway.com. 

.
.
.
.
.
.
#wannerstedt #proportions #2021 #3d #3dart #animation #satisfying #nft #drop #nfts #cryptoart #artdirection #niftygateway

Download the @Gemini app to buy ether for my drop
